# Feh Key Binding Config
#
#
#
# key definition: <action name> <key1> [<key2> [<key3>]]
# -> A maximum of 3 keys are allowed for each action
# default key binding are overwritten
#
# Each <key> is an X11 keysym (as output by xev) with optional modifier.
# For instance, C-x would be Ctrl+X, or 4-space Mod4+Space


# vim like image navigation
next_img l space Right
prev_img h BackSpace Left

# named rotate key
orient_1 r greater
orient_3 R less
# remove default actions for key `r` which is now used for rotate
reload_image C-r
render C-R
